org.opends.server.replication.plugin

Class FakeModdnOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.replication.plugin.FakeOperation
      • org.opends.server.replication.plugin.FakeModdnOperation

  • public class FakeModdnOperation
extends FakeOperation
    This class if used to build fake MODDN Operation from the historical information that stay in the entry in the database. This is useful when a LDAP server can't find a LDAP server that has already seen all its changes and therefore need to retransmit them.
